-xlEa8EqQ">Phạt Tống lộ bố văn - 伐宋露布文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/author-k8EDHIxplIZZ0LYB28XrSA">Lý Thường Kiệt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-hi%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0-t%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-dlHnmd0KjGsb0OLTGFEOjQ">Tống Lưu hiệu thư tòng quân - 送劉校書從軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/author-UC91PIpcFalgwS4PbK2Lpg">Dương Quýnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-II/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-VZIFffgurOnba3Ynh-DL1w">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam kỳ 1 - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-II/author-X22fYxIo2ceo12F3i4RIVA">Lý Thanh (II)</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
